concept Interpolation

purpose
    to handle smooth transitions between two scenes or object states

state
    a t Number
    a source Object
    a target Object

actions
    interpolate (source: Object, target: Object, t: Number) : (object: Object)
    setT (interpolation: Interpolation, t: Number) : (interpolation: Interpolation)
    start (interpolation: Interpolation) : (interpolation: Interpolation)
    stop (interpolation: Interpolation) : (interpolation: Interpolation)
